dct_description_sm: Shows transit stations, embassies, churches, recreational areas, expressway entrances and exits, educational and governmental facilities, assorted places of business, and street numbering system.
"For greater detail, see Central Moscow, 1:15,000 scale, map number 800586."
"This edition of the Central Moscow street map reflects the recent Soviet street and place name changes as of July 1986"--Verso.
Indexes, abbreviations and glossary on verso.
